Package: isparkagwise
Type: Package
Title: Agwise Modelling Framework Implemented for iSPARK Project
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Eduardo", "Garcia Bendito",
      email = "e.bendito@cgiar.org",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: The package provides a reproducible end-to-end pipeline to generate 
    fertilizer recommendations. The pipeline can be implemented for any country in 
    Africa as it relies on Africa-only data sources (iSDA Soil). The example 
    implementation relies on observational data from carob (carob-data.org) but 
    other data sources can be added as inputs.
